title: My God Someone Que Up For 3v3
body: Literally been sitting in que for half an hour and I can't find a game holy moly.

replies.body: Yea, maybe when gold funneling from 3v3 is gone. Before everyone starts bitching, Riot did something with 5v5's gold funneling and are gonna do more later. But they just don't care about 3v3 sadly ;(
